HEADWORD: Chromid
<hw>Chro"mid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a kind of
fish.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of the <fam>Chromid⟦ae⟧</fam>,
